    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/8517f41a993e5bb3148dff56e1221239.avif?t=1757038818\" width=600 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >侦探大赛官方Q群：787435549</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/3eae27b97423120ac110f88ed21ec1e9.avif?t=1757038818\" width=500 height=149 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一部可以玩的软推理群像剧视觉小说系列作品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/889f5745ae8423dfe546e10f5adf6c65.poster.avif?t=1757038818\" width=660 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/889f5745ae8423dfe546e10f5adf6c65.webm?t=1757038818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/889f5745ae8423dfe546e10f5adf6c65.mp4?t=1757038818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲爱的各位侦探：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    欢迎来到侦探大赛！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    一百位侦探齐聚一堂，在神秘大赛中斗智斗勇，侦破由顶级天才罪犯们构造的重重案件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    在大赛中胜出的侦探将得到一百万美元的奖金，还有一个终生难遇的机会在前方等待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    然而，如果罪犯赢下比赛，罪犯也将得到一百万美元……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    且不论犯下了多重的罪行，都将被无条件保释！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    那么，请开始各位的表演！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                          ——Game-Master</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/d11b65c908d876b6be31abc8c6e83fa5.poster.avif?t=1757038818\" width=660 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/d11b65c908d876b6be31abc8c6e83fa5.webm?t=1757038818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/d11b65c908d876b6be31abc8c6e83fa5.mp4?t=1757038818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《探案法》是一部视觉小说，探案机制简单易懂，你将在游戏中搜查证据，在多个选项中作出选择，解开谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全篇有一百章，共有13万9千词的文本，大约需要十小时的游玩时间（主要取决于你的阅读速度）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/fc3c0f9a9af3a6baf446276a201e7ae9.poster.avif?t=1757038818\" width=660 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/fc3c0f9a9af3a6baf446276a201e7ae9.webm?t=1757038818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/fc3c0f9a9af3a6baf446276a201e7ae9.mp4?t=1757038818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/7b8059703689137bfb7e4df03ffa92c7.avif?t=1757038818\" width=550 height=174 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原创作曲音乐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过25个可交互的案件现场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的欢乐无厘头叙事风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >百位个性十足的角色设计</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清奇的画风</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现实与荒诞融合的侦探世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幕后花絮</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关注微博</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271300/extras/70459fe7d77da6a58fcb84f1c2628da9.avif?t=1757038818\" width=600 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
